commit.message:
fix: read filename of the symbolic link

busybox and rust coreutils link to the single executable.
Relax test condition to check that /bin/sleep is a symlink
and read the expected file name from the symlink.

fix: relax test condition for TrueExe and FalsExe

Busybox and rust coreutils create symlinks to the single executable.
Test that /bin/true and /bin/false are symlinks instead of
checking that they are linked to /bin/busybox.
